{"tid":28661,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"[求救]Amazon US 退貨","createTime":"2016-12-08T05:39:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-19T16:14:19.000Z","uid":19609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5a2b9b0039f40ba4c6ef0468928226596b3ff3fe","tid":28661,"uid":19609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T05:39:36.000Z","msg":"之前係Amazon US 買左個HTC RE camera <br />\n送去集運再轉送香港。<br />\n<br />\n送到香港發現部Cam 底蓋烈開左<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bERi7PQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbERi7PQ.jpg&h=02879aa5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後send email 問 Amazon 個CS<br />\n佢話可以全數退返shipping fee from HK to US<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">有冇巴打試過因為集運地址而冇得退？</span></strong>"},{"pid":"960758b0d66af499c08670e873b5025ea1cf3cb2","tid":28661,"uid":25703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T05:44:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1c8e739f37fe80e6f3692d63fa3b21bdb53a5812","tid":28661,"uid":19609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T05:55:50.000Z","msg":"問多個問題  Fedex, UPS, DHL 邊間好"},{"pid":"dccbc94792f2ef31fbec764bcf3b67e35cc958e0","tid":28661,"uid":46030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T06:57:05.000Z","msg":"千其唔好fedex<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c103e11cb88f74d0e81bd18bbdbcea01b461319a","tid":28661,"uid":46030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T06:57:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>千其唔好fedex<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自隊半打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />