":56973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T11:18:13.000Z","msg":"香港郵局寄唔得咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f42bbb2a3d0c06f54edcd88554fb7e5156b231bf","tid":28661,"uid":6141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T11:21:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港郵局寄唔得咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有人比返錢 無所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4462d67d10847780f36e935c1fb02461d09f9f32","tid":28661,"uid":52040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T11:23:27.000Z","msg":"想請教巴打，amazon買d唔送hk既貨，<br />\n用咩集運公司可靠？<br />\n利申:想買ps2手制  電結他 等"},{"pid":"bcd7b60e29134200306071d5d8704badcd9bcb75","tid":28661,"uid":57549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T11:24:19.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"2ee4bc36786b49c5d239d5c2f46e07206e522599","tid":28661,"uid":19609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T12:19:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>香港郵局寄唔得咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有人比返錢 無所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港郵政ok, 但上網做過research, <br />\n香港郵政一個月有兩班船去美國<br />\n假設係1 號 同 15 號<br />\n<br />\n如果你咁岩2 號先寄， 咁15號先出船， 到美國應該係一個月之後既事<br />\n<br />\namazon 有個政策係 收貨後過左三十日 如果要退回就運費自理<br />\n<br />\n所以用香港郵政送得去，一定過三十日， 到時運費可能claim 唔返<br />\n<br />\n但香港郵政有個好處 就係平， 2 kg 以下 都係$80 per kg<br />\n<br />\n但重點係慢 同冇tracking code, 寄失左閣下自理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n巴打講得岩， 有人包底運費  貴一貴都比 最緊要安全送到佢手上"},{"pid":"a8bb749758a3b28aaf76319deab15a2af60ee1ef","tid":28661,"uid":19609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T12:22:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想請教巴打，amazon買d唔送hk既貨，<br />\n用咩集運公司可靠？<br />\n利申:想買ps2手制  電結他 等</blockquote><br />\n經過今次 如果佢講明唔送香港 我勸你都係香港買算<br />\n除非你已經有收到壞貨既準備<br />\n<br />\n唔係個個都咁好彩，CS 肯包運費<br />\n<br />\n之前有CASE 係唔包運費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最緊要你客氣同CS 講  問清楚晒先好退貨"},{"pid":"17da83bc66835352c1651cbe7bc4b09571dad881","tid":28661,"uid":19609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T12:23:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>貨已寄<br />\n1kg 內收我465.5 HKD<br />\n<br />\n會繼續Update, 留比下一手有相同經歷既巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n補多句， 我係用DHL 最快果個Package, 預計四日到佢手上<br />\n<br />\n現金paid 8折"},{"pid":"fe9241e5246d343bf32f31903f9d3035ed086685","tid":28661,"uid":19609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T12:27:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想請教巴打，amazon買d唔送hk既貨，<br />\n用咩集運公司可靠？<br />\n利申:想買ps2手制  電結他 等</blockquote><br />\n經過今次 如果佢講明唔送香港 我勸你都係香港買算<br />\n除非你已經有收到壞貨既準備<br />\n<br />\n唔係個個都咁好彩，CS 肯包運費<br />\n<br />\n之前有CASE 係唔包運費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最緊要你客氣同CS 講  問清楚晒先好退貨</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n仲有既就係  如果要退貨， 唔好咁傻豬用佢內置system 退貨， 一定要direct contact CS.<br />\n<br />\n因為國際退件有第二個address, 你用內置system 比你個退貨address 係只限美國境內<br />\n<br />\n當然 應該最後都會退到， 但可能要多d 時間"},{"pid":"6fe039bbb639c01744d0bfb7bae97dc0a92a17c7","tid":28661,"uid":20376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T12:30:44.000Z","msg":"我記得香港郵政有空郵同普通郵寄（應該係你講既船運），上年叫家弟幫手寄幾件厚衫去美國比我，佢貪平簡左最平個方法，10月叫佢寄，我12月底先收到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過巴打你真係好彩，cs肯退運費比你。有陣時自己本土買野都未必樣樣有得退<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cded1fba417745926fcbc4291ee4b32e5956ade","tid":28661,"uid":19609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T12:35:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我記得香港郵政有空郵同普通郵寄（應該係你講既船運），上年叫家弟幫手寄幾件厚衫去美國比我，佢貪平簡左最平個方法，10月叫佢寄，我12月底先收到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過巴打你真係好彩，cs肯退運費比你。有陣時自己本土買野都未必樣樣有得退<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔知船定飛機啦<br />\n總之半個月走唔甩  慢則好似巴打你咁兩個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5de0713045a06d1a834ebca72038c978fe66f427","tid":28661,"uid":39084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T04:52:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>香港郵局寄唔得咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有人比返錢 無所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n試過，不過運費退唔足"},{"pid":"da8811b22ed0c13dd8901db03bc4fab1177253da","tid":28661,"uid":16755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-10T14:30:06.000Z","msg":"好似最高20usd 運費補貼"},{"pid":"e51388b899b25cb2b39a78a3dd7349e44f56a6a9","tid":28661,"uid":53333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-10T15:50:33.000Z","msg":"留名睇蝕錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9546435fb78591943714949c7ab58236b6438df9","tid":28661,"uid":44486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-10T15:59:13.000Z","msg":"試過買對白色鞋<br />\n黎到已經黃左,重要有膠水跡<br />\n我即刻上網屌佢地,本身要翻寄番去<br />\n最後傾到refund +keep住對鞋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5ff00ae24e0517d0c5b9f92531324e8868e0854","tid":28661,"uid":19609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-11T07:40:25.000Z","msg":"岩岩去完旅行返黎, 可以再講下結果<br />\n<br />\n已經退返晒99% 既錢,包括貨$ 同運費<br />\n唯一蝕左少少既只係匯率<br />\n<br />\n圖後補, <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddc8d04702bb5bbc5eb9c8e083f1433d874a743c","tid":28661,"uid":36995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T16:14:19.000Z","msg":"圖呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}